name: Fast Delivery
description:
Fast Delivery is a fun and challenging runner about a food deliverer.

Who is the most productive and fastest delivery man in the city, of course it's you!
Help the deliveryman to deliver the order as soon as possible, there are many obstacles and enemies on the way. Use: scooter, balls, superman power, motorcycle.

Test your reaction, make the character jump in time and overcome obstacles and enemies. On the levels you can find special perks that change the gameplay.

Features of the game:
-40 levels
-3 locations
-cool music
-gamepad support
-funny graphics
